macros when you compile to define:
    1. endian about:
        big endian: BIG_ENDIAN
        little endian: LITTLE_ENDIAN
    2. CPU about:
        aarch64:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_CPU _aarch64
            AARCH64
        IA32 AMD46 Intel-core (any one of them):
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_CPU _x86
            X86
        S390:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_CPU _s390
            S390
        PPC32 or PPC64:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_CPU _ppc
            PPC
        ARM32 or AArch64:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_CPU _aarch32
            AARCH32

    3.OS about:
        Windows10:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_OS _win10
            WIN10
        Windows7:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_OS _win7
            WIN7
        Linux:
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_OS _linux
            LINUX
        MAC FreeBSD OpenBSD( bsd-based ):
            INCLUDE_SUFFIX_OS _bsd
            BSD

    4.bit about:
        32bit:
            BIT_32
        64bit:
            BIT_64s
